data.name: GioiDiDong Pro
data.description: B2B wholesale platform for electronics distributors with real-time inventory
data.summary: Built using microservices architecture handling 500+ concurrent transactions. Integrated with 8 warehouse management systems.
data.challenges: Synchronizing inventory across 200+ physical stores with sub-second latency requirements.
data.solution: Developed custom event-driven synchronization engine using Apache Kafka and Redis caching layer.
data.outcome: Processed $15M+ monthly transactions within first quarter, reduced inventory discrepancies by 99%.
